import React from 'react'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card';
import {} from '../img/Carouselstyle.css';
import Accordion from 'react-bootstrap/Accordion';
import { Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap';

const Cards = () => {

const realestate = [
  {
     id: 1,
     name: "House",
     Img: "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1026205392/photo/beautiful-luxury-home-exterior-at-twilight.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=HOCqYY0noIVxnp5uQf1MJJEVpsH_d4WtVQ6-OwVoeDo="
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    name: "House",
    Img: "https://image.shutterstock.com/image-photo/beautiful-exterior-newly-built-luxury-260nw-529108441.jpg"
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    name: "House",
    Img: "https://media.istockphoto.com/id/175416231/photo/cute-simple-home.jpg?b=1&s=170667a&w=0&k=20&c=beTWtD7CHAws6SwjxAMFOW7DB5WkgecBygki38giODQ="
  },
];

  return (
    <>
    <Container className='ContainerRow'>
        <Col>
      <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/real-estate-company-logo-designs-minimalist-house-inspirations-140758141.jpg" />
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>{realestate.name}</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
        {realestate.Img}
        </Card.Text>
        <Button variant="primary">Go somewhere</Button>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>

    
    </Col>

    <Col>


    <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/real-estate-company-logo-designs-minimalist-house-inspirations-140758141.jpg" />
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Card Title</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
          bulk of the card's content.
        </Card.Text>
        <Button variant="primary">Go somewhere</Button>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>

   
    </Col>

    <Col>
    <Card style={{ width: '18rem' }}>
      <Card.Img variant="top" src="https://thumbs.dreamstime.com/b/real-estate-company-logo-designs-minimalist-house-inspirations-140758141.jpg" />
      <Card.Body>
        <Card.Title>Card Title</Card.Title>
        <Card.Text>
          Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the
          bulk of the card's content.
        </Card.Text>
        <Button variant="primary">Go somewhere</Button>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>

  
    </Col>
    </Container>

    </>
  )
}

export default Cards
